Snapshot Levels
🟢 Foundation Snapshot

Examples:

Fresh server
Docker installed
Base infrastructure complete
🟢 Architecture Snapshot

Examples:

Hermes v0.2
COMM-1 completed
Jobfynder API stable
🟢 Release Snapshot

Examples:

Hermes v1.0
MVP Launch
Production Release
🟢 Pre-Migration Snapshot

Before:

PostgreSQL upgrades
Ubuntu upgrades
Docker upgrades
Major refactoring
My proposal for all Jobfynder servers

Eventually we'll have something like:

Server	Snapshot Frequency
INTEL-1 (Hermes)	At milestones + before major changes
COMM-1 (n8n/bridges)	At milestones + before workflow changes
Production Jobfynder	Before every release and major infrastructure change